   149	
   150	### 2.3 `EmitSignalInput`
   151	
   152	Callers provide this to `emit()`. The layer assigns `id`, `emittedAt`, and initial `state`.
   153	
   154	```typescript
   155	export interface EmitSignalInput {
   156	  threadId: string;
   157	  source: string;
   158	  audience: SignalAudience;
   159	  messageClass: MessageClass;
   160	  signalClass: SignalClass;
   161	  priority: SignalPriority;
   162	  summary: string;
   163	  confidence?: number;
   164	  details?: string;
   165	  replaces?: string;
   166	  expiresAtStep?: number;
