   169	
   170	**Validation rules enforced by `emit()`:**
   171	- `threadId`, `source`, `summary` must be non-empty strings
   172	- `signalClass` must be consistent with `messageClass` (e.g., `attention.raise` requires `messageClass='attention'`)
   173	- `confidence` required when `messageClass` is `'confidence'` or `'conflict'`; must be 0.0‚Äì1.0 when present
   174	- `replaces`, if set, must refer to a signal ID within the same `threadId`
   175	- `priority='critical'` signals bypass suppression regardless of window
