   216	
   217	| Signal class | Message class | Semantic | Required `confidence` range |
   218	|---|---|---|---|
   219	| `attention.raise` | attention | Flag something for another's consideration | ‚Äî |
   220	| `confidence.high` | confidence | Output is stable and well-supported | 0.8‚Äì1.0 |
   221	| `confidence.medium` | confidence | Output is reasonable but has caveats | 0.4‚Äì0.79 |
   222	| `confidence.low` | confidence | Output is speculative; coordinator should weigh carefully | 0.1‚Äì0.39 |
   223	| `confidence.blocker` | confidence | Cannot produce useful output; requires more input | 0.0 |
   224	| `conflict.active` | conflict | Conflict exists and is unresolved | any 0.0‚Äì1.0 |
   225	| `conflict.resolved` | conflict | Previously flagged conflict has been resolved | any 0.0‚Äì1.0 |
   226	| `handoff.ready` | handoff | Output is ready for downstream consumption | ‚Äî |
   227	| `handoff.partial` | handoff | Partial output available; more is coming | ‚Äî |
